# üåê sriox.com ‚Äì Self-Hosted Domain & Web Hosting Platform (Coolify + VPS)

A powerful, self-hosted subdomain and redirect platform like is-a.dev ‚Äî fully managed from your VPS.  
Users can upload websites, create redirects, and map GitHub Pages repos under your domain `sriox.com` ‚Äî all through a sleek dashboard.

---

## üöÄ Features

### üóÇÔ∏è 1. Free Static Hosting with Subdomain (like GitHub Pages)
- Users can upload a ZIP (‚â§ 35MB) containing `index.html`
- System extracts and serves the site at:  
  `yourname.sriox.com`
- Websites are stored at:  
  `/data/sites/{subdomain}/`

### üîÅ 2. Redirect Pages (sriox.com/username)
- Users can create subpages like:  
  `sriox.com/meher` ‚Üí `https://example.com/meher`
- A simple HTML file with meta-refresh is generated at:  
  `/data/subpages/{name}.html`

### üêô 3. GitHub Pages Domain Mapping (is-a.dev-style)
- Users can link their GitHub Pages repo (e.g. `username.github.io/repo`)
- Your system:
  - Stores the mapping in a JSON file or database
  - Updates Cloudflare DNS for the subdomain
  - Creates a CNAME pointing to GitHub Pages
- Example:  
  `project.sriox.com` ‚Üí `username.github.io/project`

### üßë‚Äçüíª 4. Full Dashboard (Built with React)
- Auth (email, password or Firebase)
- Upload ZIP file
- Add/edit/delete subdomains
- Create redirects
- Link GitHub Pages repos
- Show user limit status (free vs upgraded)

